# Title: Google Cloud DNS Zone Modified or Deleted
# Author: Austin Songer @austinsonger
# Date: 2021-08-15
# Level: medium
# Description: Identifies when a DNS Zone is modified or deleted in Google Cloud.
# MITRE Tactic: Impact
# Tags: attack.impact
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/cloud/gcp/audit/gcp_dns_zone_modified_or_deleted.yml

gcp.audit.method_name IN ("Dns.ManagedZones.Delete", "Dns.ManagedZones.Update", "Dns.ManagedZones.Patch")